examples.en: Has your flat got a balcony?
Their balcony looks out over the city.
examples.ru: С их балкона открывается вид на город.

examples.en: We asked for a hotel room with a balcony.
She stood on a balcony looking down into the courtyard.
examples.ru: Она стояла на балконе и смотрела вниз, во двор.

examples.en: Terry fixed herself a cold drink and sat out on the balcony.
examples.ru: Терри приготовила себе прохладительный напиток и села на балконе.

examples.en: People were making noise in the balcony overhead.
examples.ru: На балконе сверху громко шумели люди.

examples.en: She pitched over the railing of the balcony.
The balcony is festooned in ivy.
